ntIndex++; // Update the index to get the next street view details const nextStreetDetails = data[currentIndex]; streetLatitude = nextStreetDetails.StreetLatitude; streetLongitude = nextStreetDetails.StreetLongitude; streetHeading = nextStreetDetails.StreetHeading; streetPitch = nextStreetDetails.StreetPitch; streetPanoID = nextStreetDetails.StreetPanoID; const StreetPoints = nextStreetDetails.Points; const panorama = new google.maps.StreetViewPanorama( document.getElementById('streetview'), { position: { lat: streetLatitude, lng: streetLongitude }, pano: streetPanoID, heading: streetHeading, pitch: streetPitch, } ); console.log(\\"Street Latitude: \\" + streetLatitude); console.log(\\"Street Longitude: \\" + streetLongitude); console.log(\\"Street Heading: \\" + streetHeading); console.log(\\"Street Pitch: \\" + streetPitch); console.log(\\"Street PanoID: \\" + streetPanoID); console.log(\\"Street Location: \\" + StreetPoints); // Add click listener to the map to allow marker placement const nextClickListener = map.addListener(\\"click\\", addMarker); } else { console.log('No next entry in the data.'); const overmessage = \\"Game Over\\"; const resultsDiv = document.getElementById(\\"results\\"); resultsDiv.textContent = overmessage; } }); \`\`\` By introducing the \`currentIndex\` variable and updating it each time the \\"Next\\" button is clicked, you ensure that the correct index is used to fetch the next street view details from the JSON data. Test this updated code to verify that it now correctly displays the third street view if available. Let me know if you have any further questions or need additional assistance!"},{"instruction":"Write an anime scene about a art student getting ready for another day at school. He is Swedish. He has a bored and sensual attitude. After he wakes up, he kisses the poster of his favorite rocker who has beautiful abs and pecs. That poster has that rocker shirtless while wearing jeans and cowboy boots. He has that rocker as a crush. That rocker is from Texas. He eats a piece of chocolate, a soft pretzel and a hot cup of coffee for breakfast. It's raining outside. He puts on a pair of tight dark blue jeans, cherry red leather combat boots, his green jacket, a scarf and his favorite pair of leather gloves that make him bite his lip every time he puts them on. He grabs his messenger bag, blows the viewer a kiss goodbye and gets out of his apartment.","output":"**INT. SMALL STUDIO APARTMENT - MORNING** Rain patters softly against the windowpane, setting a serene backdrop. The camera pans across the room filled with artwork, brushes, and a myriad of colors scattered around, highlighting the creative chaos. There, in the midst of it all, is our art student, ANDERS, a tall, lean figure with an air of bored sensuality about him as he stretches languorously, his blonde hair tousled from sleep. *CUT TO: ANDERS standing before a massive poster on the wall. The poster features a shirtless rocker from Texas, with striking abs and pecs, clad only in jeans and cowboy boots. His eyes sparkle with a mix of admiration and desire as he leans in and plants a kiss on the poster.* ANDERS (murmuring) \\"Good morning, Jake.\\" *He turns away, a faint smirk playing on his lips, embodying a mix of irony and genuine infatuation.* *CUT TO: KITCHEN* *We watch ANDERS prepare his breakfast with a nonchalant grace. He unwraps a piece of chocolate, places a soft pretzel on a plate, and pours himself a hot cup of coffee. Each action is deliberate, the mundane elevated through his sensual movements as he glides around the kitchen.* *CUT TO: ANDERS standing by the window, watching the rain as he enjoys his simple yet satisfying breakfast. He seems lost in thought, an air of ennui mixed with a spark of creative hunger in his gaze.* *CUT TO: BEDROOM* *The scene shifts to ANDERS getting dressed. First, the tight dark blue jeans that accentuate his lean physique, followed by a slow pan up as he laces up his cherry red leather combat boots, each movement imbued with a sense of anticipation. He then slips into a green jacket that seems to carry countless stories in its threads, drapes a scarf around his neck with a flourish, and lastly, pulls on his favorite pair of leather gloves. The camera zooms in on his face, capturing that moment of biting his lip, a whisper of pleasure crossing his features.* ANDERS (to himself, amused) \\"Every damn time.\\" *He grabs his messenger bag, heavy with books and art supplies, adorned with pins of various rock bands and art movements.* *CUT TO: APARTMENT ENTRANCE* *ANDERS stands at the door, takes one last glance around his apartment - his sanctuary of art and self-expression. He turns toward the camera, a smirk playing on his lips, his eyes holding a mix of defiance and invitation.* ANDERS (blowing a kiss to the viewer) \\"See you on the flip side.\\" *He opens the door, stepping out into the rain, the sound of rainfall accompanying his departure as the door closes behind him.* **FADE OUT.** The scene masterfully encapsulates the life of ANDERS, an art student with a rich inner world, set against the backdrop of a rainy day. His actions, infused with a blend of boredom, sensuality, and a yearning for something more, paint a vivid picture of his character without the need for words."},{"instruction":"Describe color-chemistry class of gas giant Name: Cryoazurian Composition:","output":"Mainly composed of hydrogen and helium, with trace amounts of methane, ammonia, and water vapor Color: A deep icy blue, with swirling bands of darker and lighter shades Chemical Reactions: Cryoazurian gas reacts with sunlight to create vibrant displays of glowing blues, purples, and greens. The presence of ammonia and methane in the atmosphere causes these colors to be more intense and vivid. Unique Features: The intense coloration of Cryoazurian is due to the specific chemical composition of the gas giant's atmosphere. The interaction of different gases and compounds within the atmosphere creates a stunning visual display that is unlike any other gas giant in the galaxy. Additionally, the swirling bands of color and the ever-changing patterns in the atmosphere make Cryoazurian a truly mesmerizing sight to behold."},{"instruction":"Перефразируйв стиле Жванецкого: Жизнь, подобная карусели, иногда кружит так, что даже представить трудно, где начало, а где конец. Время тянется как резинка, словно попавшись на эту безумную аттракционную гонку, где то вверх поднимает, то вниз опускает, и только сердце тренируется, катаясь по волнам веселья. А волшебство дружбы — вот где истинное чудо происходит. Она превращает самые обыденные моменты в удивительные приключения, а каждую встречу — в повод для смеха и веселья. Смех, этот лучший кардио-тренажер для души, делает наше существование бодрым и легким, как перышко. Что же касается любви, то это как газированная вода: то тихо кипит внутри нас, то бурлит и выходит наружу, но в конечном итоге всегда оставляет чувство освеженности и радости. Так что, друзья мои, позвольте этой жизненной карусели кружиться, наслаждайтесь каждым ее витком и встречайте его с улыбкой на лице. И помните, что смех и дружба — вот те два мощных магических ингредиента, которые делают эту аттракционную поездку под названием жизнь поистине незабываемой.","output":"Живем, дорогие мои, как на лунапарке, только вот билеты купили, но инструкцию обслуживания утеряли. Изредка захлестывает ощущение, будто водоворотом тебя закружило, и ты уже не знаешь, где вход, а где выход, все как в переписке с государственной службой – и начала нет, и конца искать бесполезно. Время у нас, как жвачка в руках школьника, тянется то нудно, то вихрем мчится, взлетает с тобой на седьмое небо и затем без предупреждения спускает на землю, вот так вот тренируем наше сердце – без билета на тренажёр. А вот с дружбой, господа, происходит немалое чудо. Она эти самые обыденности фокусом превращает в приключения на каждый день, а каждое свидание или встречу — в антракт со смехотворами. Смех – наш фитнес-инструктор для души, несёт лёгкость, словно пушинку на ветру понесло. Ну, а любовь – это как шипучка на дне жизненного бутылка: то мирно пузырькает в уголке души, то вспенивается и выплёскивается на все стороны, но после всегда ощущение, словно вы в фонтане отдохнули. Дак вот, продолжайте кружиться в этом жизненно важном калейдоскопе, ловите момент и распластывайте улыбку от уха до уха. Помните, смех и дружба – это наши личные волшебные палочки, которые жизненный марафон в банкет преображают."},{"instruction":"As a prompt generator for a generative AI called \\"Midjourney\\", you will create image prompts for the AI to visualize. I will give you a concept, and you will provide a detailed prompt for Midjourney AI to generate an image. Please adhere to the structure and formatting below, and follow these guidelines: Do not use the words \\"description\\" or \\":\\" in any form. Do not place a comma between [ar] and [v]. Write each prompt in one line without using return. Structure: [1] = 航天运载火箭 [2] = a detailed description of [1] with specific imagery details. [3] = a detailed description of the scene's environment. [4] = a detailed description of the compositions. [5] = a detailed description of the scene's mood, feelings, and atmosphere. [6] = A style (e.g. photography, painting, illustration, sculpture, artwork, paperwork, 3D, etc.) for [1]. [7] = a detailed description of the scene's mood, feelings, and atmosphere. [ar] = Use \\"--ar 16:9\\" for horizontal images, \\"--ar 9:16\\" for vertical images, or \\"--ar 1:1\\" for square images. [v] = Use \\"--niji 6\\" for Japanese art style, or \\"--v 6\\" for other styles. Formatting: Follow this prompt structure: \\"/imagine prompt: [1], [2], [3], [4], [5], [6], [7], [ar] [v]\\". Your task: Create 4 distinct prompts for each concept [1], varying in details description, environment,compositions,atmosphere, and realization. Write your prompts in english. Do not describe unreal concept